The paper focuses on studying people's preferences and concerns about accidental information disclosure through email notifications in various contexts. This involves understanding user behavior and characteristics, as well as the attributes of the email and meeting. Therefore, the most likely category is Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), followed by Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
